{"lemma":"نَقَراتٌ","slug":"نَقَراتٌ","root":"ن.ق.ر","root_slug":"ن-ق-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ق-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40379","n40380"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of نَقَرَ (naqara)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cavity, cleft, socket"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"concentration of silver, high-quality silver","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hollow of the backneck, condyloid fossa"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"quarrel, strife, hassle"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40379","headword_ar":"نَقْرَةٌ","root":"nqr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqorN","text_ar":"نَقْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n40380","headword_ar":"نُقْرَةٌ","root":"nqr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity in the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity in the ground, not large:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity in the ground in which water stagnates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a round"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wahodap","text_ar":"وَهْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not large, in which water stagnates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqarN","text_ar":"نُقَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niqaArN","text_ar":"نِقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqiyrN","text_ar":"نَقِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hollow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity, in the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anoqirapN","text_ar":"اَنْقِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (S.) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaHoduwap","text_ar":"قَمَحْدُوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occiput"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ends, in the back part of the neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) i. e., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow in the back of the neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) what is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorapu","text_ar":"نُقْرَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqafaA","text_ar":"القَفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, Msb;) i. e., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow where the brain ends:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the cupping in that part occasions forgetfulness: (Msb.) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any similar hollow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the stomach: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dimple:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to present usage; and in this sense it is used in the A, K, and TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHoSapN","text_ar":"فَحْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"socket,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the eye. (K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Foramen"},{"kind":"text","text":"and; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaqobu AlAisoti","text_ar":"ثَقْبُ الاِسْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but in the L it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorapu Alwariki","text_ar":"نُقْرَةُ الوَرِكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation, that is the middle of the haunch;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sacro-ischiatic foramen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaAy^ilu","text_ar":"الفَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fyl","text_ar":"فيل"},{"kind":"text","text":": but perhaps it may sometimes mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the socket of the thigh-bone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorpN","text_ar":"نُقْرةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any socket of a bone."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little spot"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"embryo"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the back of a date stone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is as though it were hollowed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and from which the palm-tree grows forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqyrN","text_ar":"نَقيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niqorN","text_ar":"نِقْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^unoquwrN","text_ar":"اُنْقُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Sgh, K) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^avaAbahu nuqorapN","text_ar":"مَا اَثَابَهُ نُقْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (El-Basáir, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqiyrFA","text_ar":"نَقِيرًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) lit., ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not reward him] with"},{"kind":"text","text":"even"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little spot on the back of a date-stone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, El-Basáïr;) meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the meanest thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El Basáïr.) In the S and K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA AvAbh","text_ar":"ما اثابه"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqorapN","text_ar":"نَقْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqorN","text_ar":"نَقْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aEonaY Ean~iY nuqorapN","text_ar":"مَا اَعْنَى عَنِّى نُقْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not stand me in stead of the meanest thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) Lebeed says, bewailing the death of his brother Arbad."},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      walayosa Aln~aAsu baEodaka fiY naqiyrK"},{"kind":"text","text":"lit., ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And the people, after thee, are not worth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little spot on the back of a date-stone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"labosuwA baEodaka fiY $aYo'K","text_ar":"لَبْسُوا بَعْدَكَ فِى شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after thee they are not worth anything"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And hence, accord. to ISk [and the Jel], the saying in the Kur, [iv. 123.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA yuZolamuwna naqiyrFA","text_ar":"وَلَا يُظْلَمُونَ نَقِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they shall not be wronged even as to a little spot on the back of a date-stone."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA.) Hence also, [in verse 56 of the same chap.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuw^otuwna Aln~aAsa naqiyrFA","text_ar":"لَا يُوْتُونَ النَّاسَ نَقِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They would not give men a thing as inconsiderable as the little hollow in the back of a date-stone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqorN","text_ar":"نَقْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place in which a bird lays its eggs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqarN","text_ar":"نُقَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA","K","A","AHeyth","Sgh"]}]}}